  "elapsed_s": 201.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was in-- I was in the electrical kommando.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we marched into the electrical shack, where the construction was over there, to, like, a company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Siemens-Halske was the name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Siemens-Halske was like a subcontractor for the telephone company.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember that in the beginning over there, there were all balloons around the plant.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later on, when the airplanes came, they started to take away the balloons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if they shot them down, or-- there were not any balloons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in every intersection there was like an incinerator, and then there was an alarm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They turned on the incinerator, so it smoked up the whole plant with smoke-- that the enemy should not see what it is in there, in that plant.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was an alarm.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
